data.description: Welcome to this beautifully maintained move in ready home that is light and bright just waiting for a buyer. The first floor has a nice office space, formal dining room, sunroom and family room which is open to the breakfast area and kitchen.  Upstairs there are five spacious bedrooms that includes a huge primary bedroom and bathroom suite.  This home has great attention to detail with crown molding throughout the first floor, a tray ceiling in the dining room and decorative backsplash in the kitchen.  There is neutral paint throughout, the primary bathroom has a new tub and is nicely updated with a tile shower, all new toilets, new floors in the hall bath and powder room, architectural roof installed in 2020.
